author: National Geographic
description:
Avoiding microplastics can feel like an insurmountable task, but there are small changes you can make to reduce exposure. 

Watch What Do Microplastics Do To My Body?—the latest episode of What Does X Do To My Body on the Nat Geo YouTube channel.
title: How can you reduce your exposure to microplastics? #WhatDoesXDoToMyBody

author: National Geographic
description: This is the unforgettable stunt that inspired @DavidBlaine  to travel the world and learn seemingly impossible feats from local experts. Watch the final two episodes of David Blaine: Do Not Attempt this Sunday at 9/8c on National Geographic. Stream next day on Disney+ and Hulu.
title: Discover more about the journey to David Blaine: Do Not Attempt #DavidBlaineDoNotAttempt

author: National Geographic
description:
David Blaine sits down with National Geographic to discuss his groundbreaking new series, Do Not Attempt.  In this exclusive interview, Blaine details the incredible journey that has defined his career as one of the greatest magicians and endurance artists of all time, culminating in this thrilling new endeavor. From picking up his first deck of cards to breaking the world record for holding his breath, Blaine explains his motivation, inspiration from greats like Houdini, and what inspired him to create this brand new series.
